# Critical fixes for Railway deployment

## 1. Add /api/health endpoint to flask_app.py

Add this after the existing /health endpoint:

```python
@app.route('/api/health', methods=['GET'])
def api_health_check():
    """API health check endpoint for Railway."""
    return jsonify({
        "status": "healthy",
        "message": "Soccer Chemistry API is running",
        "version": "1.0.0"
    })
```

